_sText:
This is just a simple building that I created a while ago for my unfinished map de_inner-city. I then decided to use it as a prefab in other map creations of mine, so I might as well let others use it so they don't decompile my maps :P

The building is unaccessible, there is no back, only front, so I recommend you place this somewhere in your map, where the player will not be able to access or see the back of it.

Modify & use this as you wish.
